com.inmobi.messaging

Class ClientConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inmobi.messaging.ClientConfig

  • public class ClientConfig
extends Object
    Provides access to Configuration parameters for the messaging client. Configuration parameters are defined as name, value pairs.
